WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.440 --> 00:00:01.451
Good morning, family!

00:00:01.789 --> 00:00:04.844
Praise the Lord, it is day 45 of praying in a row.

00:00:04.844 --> 00:00:10.529
I know I have skipped a couple, but we are pretty much dead on 45, so praise the Lord.

00:00:10.867 --> 00:00:13.391
I have some things on my heart today.

00:00:13.693 --> 00:00:20.504
I was praying and the Lord showed me some things in the spirit to pray about today, so we're going to get right to it.

00:00:20.672 --> 00:00:54.209
I want to backtrack a little bit and talk about when the Lord told me that He was bringing the cure for cancer to the world and the body of Christ.

00:01:05.340 --> 00:01:06.090
He said this has plagued generations for too long now.

00:01:08.674 --> 00:01:21.220
He said, 'Son, the cure for cancer is out there.

00:01:21.220 --> 00:01:52.725
' He said that evil men in power have held it back for material gain, and He said, 'I'm going to crush them, the ones that have held back the cure.

00:01:52.725 --> 00:02:21.640
' I saw a man in a laboratory mixing this stuff up, and he found a greater cure for cancer.

00:02:21.960 --> 00:02:26.024
It was a daily supplement that you take to prevent it and cure it.

00:02:42.818 --> 00:02:43.910
The Lord gave supernatural wisdom to this person.

00:02:43.920 --> 00:02:58.428
While he was in this laboratory mixing this supplement, the Lord showed me that it was just a little bit of this and a little bit of that.

00:02:58.428 --> 00:03:27.080
People have told me, 'Oh, it's Ivermectin' and all this other stuff, but that is not what I saw.

00:03:41.661 --> 00:03:41.946
I saw a supplement that was a preventative and a cure coming in the future.

00:03:41.946 --> 00:03:55.493
Whenever I was praying, the Lord showed me to pray for Robert F.

00:03:55.493 --> 00:03:57.535
Kennedy Jr..

00:03:57.535 --> 00:04:06.422
He told me to intercede for Robert F.

00:04:06.422 --> 00:04:09.560
Kennedy Jr.

00:04:26.960 --> 00:04:51.240
because attacks were coming against him because of the freedom that he wants to bring to the FDA and the food industry to expose the darkness that has been in place worldwide.

00:04:51.240 --> 00:05:07.360
It started out of America and went into Europe and Asia.

00:05:07.360 --> 00:05:27.540
The Lord showed me it had tentacles for corruption, poisoning people through our foods and environmental factors.

00:05:27.540 --> 00:05:38.025
There's a lot of corruption intended to depopulate the world.

00:05:44.160 --> 00:05:58.189
The Lord showed me not everything is good with him, but he will expose a lot of the darkness.

00:05:58.189 --> 00:06:44.348
There are roots of things that are not all good, so I'm not sitting here on the Kennedy bandwagon, but he has an assignment to fulfill to expose darkness that the enemy has tried to bring to shorten human life.

00:06:44.348 --> 00:06:59.108
There are plenty of resources on this Earth to sustain life beyond 8 billion or 14 billion.

00:07:08.373 --> 00:07:08.627
Whatever they say about depopulation agendas—those are evil things.

00:07:12.569 --> 00:07:23.240
The Lord knew what we needed before our little peanut brains tried to figure it out.

00:07:23.240 --> 00:07:27.436
God is all-sufficient.

00:07:27.436 --> 00:07:36.160
It didn't shock Him that there are 8 billion people.

00:07:36.160 --> 00:07:42.876
God is a God of surplus.

00:07:49.435 --> 00:07:51.726
This Earth is never a shock to Him.

00:07:51.726 --> 00:07:59.875
It's greed and demonic, reprobate thinking.

00:08:02.463 --> 00:08:10.720
These men in high power are influenced by demonic spirits.

00:08:19.139 --> 00:08:34.253
I can't mention their names, but these men are buying up farmland and causing corruption for material gain, joining up with the devil.

00:08:39.587 --> 00:08:55.879
I have seen certain men in meetings with the devil, and they are influenced because he has given them power and wealth.

00:08:55.879 --> 00:09:04.860
Wealth brings influence so they can maneuver their plans into motion.

00:09:04.860 --> 00:09:24.057
They don't listen to the poor, they listen to the rich, and the rich have power.

00:09:24.057 --> 00:09:38.360
That is why God wants to raise up godly men and women of influence.

00:09:40.013 --> 00:09:46.831
You have the Greens and Mardel—the Hobby Lobby people.

00:09:46.831 --> 00:09:55.930
They are good Christian people who love the Lord.

00:09:55.930 --> 00:10:20.767
You have people of influence with money who are able to help the body of Christ, like they helped Oral Roberts University.

00:10:25.851 --> 00:10:34.816
The Lord is going to raise up new billionaires.

00:10:43.343 --> 00:10:48.240
You may not like that word, but get over it.

00:10:48.240 --> 00:11:12.391
Billionaires are going to have great influence in the world's economy to help bring forth God's agenda.

00:11:23.080 --> 00:12:17.943
Just as the devil has had his hand on certain individuals, God is going to raise up godly generals in the army of God who have influence to say, 'No, you're not going to do this,' because they have the finances to back them.

00:12:17.943 --> 00:12:24.520
It takes money to get the ball rolling.

00:12:24.520 --> 00:12:47.720
They don't listen to the poor man; they listen to the rich man making and pushing the laws through evil plans.

00:12:47.720 --> 00:13:07.255
They say, 'If you don't do this, we're not going to fund your candidacy.

00:13:07.255 --> 00:13:21.229
' You need godly men and women to say, 'You are going to put godly laws into motion or we are not going to help you.

00:13:21.229 --> 00:13:25.485
' Money talks.

00:13:43.645 --> 00:13:48.760
I got off on that, but the Lord told me it is about praying for Robert F.

00:13:48.760 --> 00:13:51.629
Kennedy Jr.

00:13:51.629 --> 00:13:58.960
because there are plans to not let him get in.

00:14:17.805 --> 00:14:18.030
We must pray for him so that he can expose darkness.

00:14:18.030 --> 00:14:42.805
I saw that his agenda to expose darkness was personal to him, something close to his heart.

00:14:42.805 --> 00:14:58.519
I don't study these candidates; the Lord just said this is personal to him.

00:14:59.310 --> 00:15:27.108
A long time ago, I told you I was interceding for a company for which the Lord gave me a name.

00:15:37.297 --> 00:15:37.714
I birthed this out in the spirit.

00:15:37.714 --> 00:15:53.235
I prayed over Protandim for a long time before Protandim ever existed.

00:15:53.235 --> 00:16:08.903
I heard the word 'Protandim' in the spirit and didn't understand it.

00:16:08.903 --> 00:16:37.040
I had my wife help me Google it because I didn't know how to spell it, but the Holy Spirit kept telling me the name Protandim.

00:16:44.325 --> 00:16:47.630
I interceded for Protandim for years without knowing what it was.

00:17:00.319 --> 00:17:00.819
I was in my 20s.

00:17:07.700 --> 00:17:22.227
The Lord said, 'Just keep praying over it; I need this product to come forth.

00:17:22.227 --> 00:17:33.335
' Years later, He said, 'It's been birthed, son.

00:17:33.335 --> 00:17:38.891
Your job is finished.

00:17:38.891 --> 00:17:53.868
' I searched for it and, sure enough, it was a product.

00:17:53.868 --> 00:18:12.497
I still don't know much about what it does, but I did my job.

00:18:12.497 --> 00:18:22.920
I saw the cure for cancer again today.

00:18:22.920 --> 00:18:43.700
I saw a demonic hand with long black nails holding it hostage, trying to block it from the people.

00:18:55.200 --> 00:18:55.545
It was a demonic stronghold.

00:18:57.615 --> 00:19:18.320
The Lord told me to come against that stronghold with the prayer warriors, to raise a standard and break it free.

00:19:18.320 --> 00:19:21.130
Pray for Robert F.

00:19:21.130 --> 00:19:24.788
Kennedy Jr.

00:19:32.270 --> 00:19:39.719
to bring forth freedom from the corruption of pesticides and chemtrails.

00:19:39.719 --> 00:19:51.100
There will be a change; I have seen it.

00:19:51.100 --> 00:20:05.876
God is going to bring this as a sign of mercy to this generation.

00:20:05.876 --> 00:20:15.760
Cancer is demonic; the way it expands is demonic.

00:20:22.234 --> 00:20:50.620
The cure is out there and they know it, but this is a greedy pharmakeia agenda to keep back something that should have been out years ago.

00:20:50.620 --> 00:20:56.314
We lift up Robert F.

00:20:56.314 --> 00:20:59.340
Kennedy Jr.

00:20:59.340 --> 00:21:08.771
before You in the name of Jesus.

00:21:08.771 --> 00:21:25.600
We thank You, Lord, that he is protected and called for such a time as this.

00:21:30.269 --> 00:21:45.525
We thank You that all evil agendas will be uncovered and that You are raising up men and women of integrity.

00:21:57.160 --> 00:22:05.960
We tell that demonic hand holding back the things God has for His people to release them now in Jesus' name!

00:22:14.946 --> 00:22:19.908
We command those people to be removed—like an Ananias of fire if need be.

00:22:26.229 --> 00:22:28.343
I thank You that all corruption is exposed.

00:22:32.840 --> 00:22:44.926
We call the cure for cancer to come forth in the name of Jesus.

00:22:44.926 --> 00:23:07.945
Just as every vaccination once eradicated diseases, this will be a thing of the past.

00:23:07.945 --> 00:23:12.486
At last, at last!

00:23:12.486 --> 00:23:21.143
We call forth the healing power of God.

00:23:21.589 --> 00:23:44.888
We expose what's being put in our food, our water, and the things causing the explosion in autism—one in 144, maybe more now.

00:23:50.946 --> 00:24:02.200
We speak to the symptoms of cancer, diabetes, heart disease, brain clots, tumors, and strokes.

00:24:14.225 --> 00:24:14.500
We speak healing and wholeness.

00:24:14.500 --> 00:24:21.143
By Your stripes, we are healed.

00:24:22.969 --> 00:24:37.929
We thank You that the demonic stronghold holding back godly wisdom for supplements is broken.

00:24:51.695 --> 00:24:54.514
We eradicate this disease in the name of Jesus.

00:25:08.360 --> 00:25:10.907
You are parting the seas just as You did for Moses.

00:25:10.907 --> 00:25:18.070
All hidden things will be revealed.

00:25:18.320 --> 00:25:56.440
The FDA will get out of the way, and You will put godly men and women over these organizations.

00:25:56.440 --> 00:26:06.606
You are removing the Pharaohs of our generation.

00:26:06.606 --> 00:26:22.440
Father, we thank You for bringing it to pass.

00:26:22.440 --> 00:26:32.840
Our eyes are always on You, Jesus.

00:27:24.053 --> 00:27:24.606
You are our healer and deliverer.

00:27:24.606 --> 00:27:38.900
We thank You that Elon Musk is radically born again.

00:27:38.900 --> 00:27:53.000
Men of great wealth will be saved for the glory of God.

00:27:53.000 --> 00:28:12.383
They will use things like Starlink to bring the Gospel throughout the whole world.

00:28:12.383 --> 00:29:06.109
I thank You for a supernatural parting of the Red Sea for him, that he would have a visitation from You and know that Jesus is the Messiah.

00:29:06.109 --> 00:29:38.330
We pray that any demonic women sent to snare him would be removed and that godly people would help him.

00:29:38.330 --> 00:29:48.884
We thank You for protection over President Trump.

00:29:48.884 --> 00:30:21.344
He is covered and controlled by the Holy Spirit, with wisdom like Solomon.

00:30:21.344 --> 00:30:32.589
We pray for supernatural wisdom to turn things around.

00:30:32.589 --> 00:30:39.280
We pray for Robert F.

00:30:39.280 --> 00:30:42.093
Kennedy Jr.

00:30:42.093 --> 00:30:50.800
again, that godly wisdom would flow over him.

00:30:50.800 --> 00:31:01.039
You are removing obstacles in their paths.

00:31:01.039 --> 00:31:34.199
We apply the blood of Jesus over Donald Trump's cabinet, his family, his wife, and his children.

00:31:34.199 --> 00:31:54.114
No weapon formed against him shall prosper.

00:31:54.114 --> 00:32:36.230
We pray for supernatural protection through January; there will be no attempts on his life.

00:32:36.240 --> 00:32:51.155
We thank You for godly wisdom to turn around finances.

00:32:51.155 --> 00:33:16.294
We bless Israel and the peace of Jerusalem.

00:33:16.294 --> 00:33:42.770
We pray for Benjamin Netanyahu to have godly wisdom.

00:34:18.600 --> 00:34:18.929
I call the hostages freed in Jesus' name.

00:34:18.929 --> 00:34:32.510
I see the border of Syria—I call them free!

00:34:32.510 --> 00:35:00.200
We thank You that the wealth of the sinner is laid up for the righteous.

00:35:00.200 --> 00:35:08.584
Let it go now in Jesus' name!

00:35:08.584 --> 00:35:27.616
When I took authority over the wealth transfer, I saw frogs with big warts—like toads—jumping away.

00:35:27.616 --> 00:35:39.299
No more nights with the frogs!

00:35:39.299 --> 00:35:47.440
I hear a turnaround in the spirit.

00:36:01.030 --> 00:36:01.280
I feel a wave of financial blessing.

00:36:01.280 --> 00:36:17.213
There is a parting in the sky; no more holding back finances.

00:36:17.213 --> 00:36:33.760
There will be a torrential downpour of glory and finances upon the church.

00:36:33.760 --> 00:36:45.089
As you sowed in the past, you'll reap at last.

00:37:06.800 --> 00:37:09.089
Great finances will pour through your hands to bring in the spoils of the lost.

00:37:09.419 --> 00:37:15.820
The glory is here!

00:37:15.820 --> 00:37:20.399
Receive it in Jesus' name.

00:37:22.937 --> 00:37:28.524
The silver and the gold are Mine, says the Lord.

00:37:28.716 --> 00:37:43.219
Get ready for manifestations of divine power.

00:37:43.599 --> 00:37:49.628
The days of lack are over.

00:37:49.628 --> 00:37:59.060
Be in step with the Spirit.

00:38:04.887 --> 00:38:09.819
This is part of the end-time harvest plan.

00:38:09.819 --> 00:38:14.335
Oh, the wealth transfer!

00:38:14.335 --> 00:38:20.657
It is the goodness of God.

00:38:20.657 --> 00:38:29.959
He has laid up treasures for you.

00:38:29.959 --> 00:38:36.571
Restitution for all you have gone through!

00:38:36.571 --> 00:38:47.660
If the thief has been found, he must repay sevenfold.

00:38:47.660 --> 00:38:54.583
Make him restore what he stole!

00:38:54.583 --> 00:39:01.440
I am speaking to the remnant.

00:39:08.938 --> 00:39:11.137
There is blessing in Goshen and Canaan, but torment in Egypt.

00:39:16.710 --> 00:39:28.400
The church is going to walk in a blessing and healing anointing like never before.

00:39:35.416 --> 00:39:49.200
The world will get darker, but the church will be a spotless bride, shining like the noonday sun.

00:39:49.200 --> 00:40:00.880
The world will see it and run to it.

00:40:00.880 --> 00:40:18.080
As for me and my house, we will serve the Lord.

00:40:18.080 --> 00:40:31.864
Great financial blessing will come to those the Lord can trust—the remnant.

00:40:31.864 --> 00:40:50.187
I see a storm coming on the East Coast, but that is not for you.

00:40:59.133 --> 00:41:05.208
Just as there was darkness in Egypt but light in Goshen, this is a type and shadow.

00:41:05.208 --> 00:41:18.293
God has a million ways to get you a million dollars overnight.

00:41:18.293 --> 00:41:22.090
The light is getting lighter.

00:41:29.151 --> 00:41:29.453
We are the great harvesters.

00:41:29.453 --> 00:41:43.146
Angel armies are taking the blinders off your loved ones' eyes.

00:41:43.146 --> 00:41:56.280
They are coming home—from Elon Musk to Taylor Swift.

00:41:56.280 --> 00:42:12.250
There will be a great harvest, even in Hollywood, the Senate, and the House.

00:42:12.250 --> 00:42:24.800
There will be prayer services in the Oval Office.

00:42:24.800 --> 00:42:41.326
There will be brush arbor churches throughout the world.

00:42:41.326 --> 00:42:52.055
Healings beyond wildest dreams will manifest.

00:42:52.055 --> 00:42:59.350
Get your heart ready; Jesus is coming.

00:42:59.635 --> 00:43:04.170
This is the last push.

00:43:14.680 --> 00:43:21.620
God has set the revival in motion for a harvest of souls.

00:43:27.066 --> 00:43:40.760
I see the bride marching, joining together as one, being taken up before the Father.

00:43:45.090 --> 00:43:45.880
The Rapture is soon.

00:43:45.880 --> 00:44:08.831
We are bringing people in from the ends of the Earth, then we are going home.

00:44:08.831 --> 00:44:18.894
We are the victorious, glorious church.

00:44:18.894 --> 00:44:31.320
We are joint heirs with Jesus Christ, sons and daughters of the Most High.

00:44:31.320 --> 00:44:36.106
No more bondage or satanic oppression.

00:44:36.106 --> 00:44:43.667
We are without spot or wrinkle.

00:44:43.667 --> 00:44:56.023
Judgment begins in the house of the Lord, but He is raising up new Davids.

00:44:56.023 --> 00:45:05.754
Believe God for a big ending to 2024 and 2025.

00:45:05.754 --> 00:45:13.789
It is light in Canaan and dark in Egypt.

00:45:13.789 --> 00:45:16.994
Praise the Lord!

00:45:16.994 --> 00:45:24.559
That word fell in like a wave.

00:45:41.689 --> 00:45:41.858
It is fun being a Christian!

00:45:56.200 --> 00:45:56.420
If you're new, thank you for joining us.

00:46:07.773 --> 00:46:07.955
I pray your fire was fanned.

00:46:07.955 --> 00:46:13.933
God is a good God.

00:46:16.975 --> 00:46:27.910
The world will go through things, but we go from glory to glory.

00:46:27.910 --> 00:46:42.880
If you spend time with Him, He will tell you about the Rapture and the glory.

00:46:42.880 --> 00:46:56.920
He is not a 'wife beater' who wants to beat you; He brings His glory.

00:46:56.920 --> 00:47:05.720
Please subscribe to our YouTube channel; it helps the algorithm.

00:47:15.415 --> 00:47:17.110
My wife said we have 65,000 people on TikTok.

00:47:19.260 --> 00:47:27.016
I cannot stand TikTok, but young people are watching and getting saved.

00:47:28.668 --> 00:47:36.416
You can find our links in the description—Instagram, Facebook, TikTok, and my X, Elon.

00:47:38.765 --> 00:47:48.729
I don't go on them much; my son and wife take care of it.

00:47:49.404 --> 00:47:53.577
Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:47:54.526 --> 00:47:59.145
Jesus loves you, and we will see you tomorrow.

00:47:59.145 --> 00:47:59.891
God bless you.
